title: Green Papaya Farm Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, International, Organic, Raw, Juice bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An organic restaurant that uses fresh farm produce, and the herbs used are grown from the owner's garden. Offers a unique raw menu from the patch. No pre-made sauces, flavor enhancer, or MSG. Vegans please inquire about options and inform HappyCow.
